pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: ʻOku tanaki fakahangatonu ʻa e fakamatala ʻoku ʻasi ʻi he Dashboard ko ʻeni mei he ngaahi tali ki he savea pea ʻoku ʻikai maʻu ia mei he ngaahi fakamatala fakasitetisitika ʻo e fonua pe ngaahi fakamatala fakaʻofisiale. ʻOku ne fakafofongaʻi ʻa e ngaahi fakakaukau naʻe fakahaaʻi ʻe he kakai kei talavou ʻi he taimi ʻo e savea, pea ko ha faʻahinga aofangatuku pe mei he ngaahi tali ko ʻeni ko e fatongia ia ʻo e tokotaha fakaʻaongaʻi, kae ʻikai ko e PMNCH. ʻOku tukupa ʻa e PMNCH ke fakaʻapaʻapaʻi, poupouʻi mo maluʻi ʻa e ngaahi totonu mo e tuʻunga lelei ʻo e niʻihi fakafoʻituitui kotoa pe. ʻOku ʻi ai ha ngaahi fakakaukau ʻoku fakahaaʻi ʻi he ngaahi tali ʻo e savea pe ngaahi naunau kuo pulusi mei he Dashboard ko ʻeni ʻoku fepaki mo e tukupa ko ʻeni ʻoku ʻikai poupouʻi ia ʻe he PMNCH.

wra03a-title: Ko e meʻa ʻoku fie maʻu ʻe he
wra03a-subtext: Maʻu ʻa e ngaahi tali ki he 1.2 million ʻi he Dashboard ko ʻeni, ko ha meʻangaue makehe ʻoku ne fakafehokotaki ʻa e leʻo ʻo e kakai fefine mo e fanau fefine mo e ngaahi faingamalie taʻe fakangatangata ʻo e fakaikiiki fakaʻilekitulonika.
pmn01a-subtext: ʻOku talitali lelei koe ki he Dashboard ʻa e "meʻa ʻoku fie maʻu ʻe he kakai kei talavou"! ʻOku ʻomi ʻe he meʻangaue fengaueʻaki ko ʻeni ha fakatata ʻo e ngaahi tali mo e ngaahi fakakaukau ʻoku tau tanaki mei he kakai kei talavou taʻu 10-24 ʻi he funga ʻo e mamani. Ko e uho ʻo e ngaue ko ha fehuʻi ʻoku ʻikai hano ngataʻanga: "ke fakaleleiʻi ʻeku tuʻunga lelei, ʻoku ou fie maʻu ..." Kuo tali ʻeni ʻe he toʻu tupu mei he funga ʻo e māmaní, ʻo tau maʻu ai ha ngaahi ʻilo makehe ki heʻenau ngaahi fie maʻú, ʻamanakí, mo ʻenau ngaahi fakaʻamú. Vakaiʻi ʻa e fakamatala, ʻiloʻi ʻa e ngaahi talanoa ʻi mui ʻi he ngaahi mataʻifika, pea kau fakataha mo kimautolu ʻi he ngaahi leʻo ʻo e kakai kei talavou ʻe toko 1.8 billion ʻi he funga ʻo e mamani. Ke ʻilo lahi ange fekauʻaki mo e ngaue, hu ki he http://www.1point8.org.
